import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'

const Container = styled.div`
    height: 60px;
`
const Wrapper = styled.div`
    padding: 10px 20px;
`
const Left = styled``
const Center = styled``
const Right = styled``

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Wrapper>
        <Left>left</Left>
        <Center>right</Center>
        <Right></Right>
        </Wrapper>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Navbar
